    "body": "Sorry it looks like your database has become corrupted.\n\nFor now the best thing to do is delete it by adding `--purge-db` to your beacon node flags and resyncing the database with checkpoint sync: https://lighthouse-book.sigmaprime.io/checkpoint-sync.html\n\nBefore deleting it could be helpful to us if you could save the logs from `/var/lib/lighthouse/beacon/logs` and send them to us (DM me on Discord, or email them to `$firstname@sigmaprime.io`)\n\nThanks",
